%% Diagram: Contract And Release Flow
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Domain as Domain team
  participant Contract as Contract artifact
  participant Registry as Registry
  participant Consumer as Consumer team
  participant Release as Release pipeline

  Domain->>Contract: Evolve API, event, or package surface
  Domain->>Release: Propose breaking change (RFC or ADR)
  Release->>Contract: Apply semver bump policy
  Contract->>Registry: Publish client, schema, or tarball
  Registry-->>Consumer: Resolve compatible range with lockfile
  Consumer->>Consumer: Integrate via adapter at boundary
  Note over Consumer,Contract: Deprecation window or release train for incompatible bumps
